1855 元，最低为 355 元，若按上海体育场 7.2 万座位数计算，单在上海一地，五月天就吸金超 6 亿。五月天在内地开了近 50 场演唱会，除演唱会门票所带来的不菲收益外，五月天的乐队周边、演唱会荧光棒等也成为二手交易市场的宠儿。据南都大数据研究院数据，2023 年「五月天」演出强度极高，国内外至少安排了 68 场演唱会，其中 9 、 10 、 11 月更连续保持月均超 8 场的节奏，估算全年在中国内地吸金已达 29.6 亿元。上海市文旅局执法总队回复五月天假唱风波调查：未发现违法行为 _ 腾讯新闻"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-7bc848f8b78f85c64aa5740c7ce87559_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "46 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/655688435"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI+rGwpNPAgroHEAMaCTEwNzk4NjM0MCCB//yxBjAAOKwCQA5yCTY1NTY4ODQzNXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "15_1715468772.927897", "card_id": "Q_655438016", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 35}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价《星穹铁道》波提欧的配音演员彭博的配音表现?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-92a5452e077c5459362c89b66f572919_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "45 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/655438016"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I+rGwpNPAgroHEAMaCTEwNzkzMDQ2MCDW+fCxBjAAOCdAD3IJNjU1NDM4MDE2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_1715468772.928144", "card_id": "Q_655516220", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 86}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "职场上从底层很难爬起来的本质原因是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-3f843e7d3c1af72c4e090eed1d2009d5_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "45 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/655516220"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI+